des:
Use Alexa to voice control your Thaleos products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
1. Download our "My Thaleos" app in app market, then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in "My Thaleos" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable "My Thaleos" skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say "Search complete";
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
"Alexa, set temperature to 18°C."
"Alexa, change Thaleos to eco mode."
"Alexa, turn off the Thaleos thermostat."
"Alexa, turn on the Thaleos thermostat."
